post_text:
Do I need to apply for P-EBT benefits? Families with children who receive CalFresh, CalWORKs, Medi-Cal, or Foster Care benefits do NOT need to apply for P-EBT benefits. Families will receive their P-EBT card in the mail between about May 12-22.
*Families with children who are eligible for free or reducedpriced school meals and who did not receive their P-EBT card in the mail must apply before June 30, 2020. More details on how to apply are coming soon!
Learn more at https://buff.ly/3dP8nbV

Students were thrilled to show off their learning to their families as doors were opened and teachers welcomed our amazing Whitaker families into their classrooms. It is inspiring to see so many students proudly pointing our their work to their families, knowing that what students accomplish now as kids will contribute to their success in high school, college, and life! Be proud, Sharks!

post_text: Charles G. Emery School held their Open House on Thursday, April 25th. The Emery scholars were proud to share their work with their families. Classrooms were filled with writing, science projects, artwork, and more. Some students even modeled using robots. We also had a Book Fair and Science Fair. A special thanks to teachers, students, staff and parents for making this event a huge success.
text: Charles G. Emery School held their Open House on Thursday, April 25th. The Emery scholars were proud to share their work with their families. Classrooms were filled with writing, science projects, artwork, and more. Some students even modeled using robots. We also had a Book Fair and Science Fair. A special thanks to teachers, students, staff and parents for making this event a huge success.
